upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-4-test-4-part-1-2023-08-13-18-09-52/45.mp3","time_start":112.83,"time_end":113.97},{"position":46,"content":"Do we suggest an amount?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-4-test-4-part-1-2023-08-13-18-09-52/46.mp3","time_start":114.2,"time_end":116.75},{"position":47,"content":"Or does it seem a bit unfair?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-4-test-4-part-1-2023-08-13-18-09-52/47.mp3","time_start":116.75,"time_end":119.46},{"position":48,"content":"No, I think people welcome it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-4-test-4-part-1-2023-08-13-18-09-52/48.mp3","time_start":119.46,"time_end":121.67},{"position":49,"content":"We suggested 6 dollars last time, is that okay?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-4-test-4-part-1-2023-08-13-18-09-52/49.mp3","time_start":121.67,"time_end":125.42},{"position":50,"content":"Yeah, plenty, I would have thought,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-4-test-4-part-1-2023-08-13-18-09-52/50.mp3","time_start":125.42,"time_end":127.62},{"position":51,"content":"which should leave us with about 90 dollars.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-4-test-4-part-1-2023-08-13-18-09-52/51.mp3","time_start":127.62,"time_end":131.28},{"position":52,"content":"Have you any ideas for presents?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-4-test-4-part-1-2023-08-13-18-09-52/52.mp3","time_start":131.5,"time_end":133.69},{"position":53,"content":"Well, I've been having a little think.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-4-test-4-part-1-2023-08-13-18-09-52/53.mp3","time_start":133.69,"time_end":136.75},{"position":54,"content":"I thought...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/u